<span id="freeTextContainer13380056971513001171">Humorous to horrifying, this is a page-turner. I&apos;m not a big short story fan overall, but these vignettes read like satisfying Aesop&apos;s Fables, with many all-too familiar scenarios that draw you in and leave you with the perfectly placed endings.</span>
  <span id="freeText13380056971513001171" style="display:none">Humorous to horrifying, this is a page-turner. I'm not a big short story fan overall, but these vignettes read like satisfying Aesop's Fables, with many all-too familiar scenarios that draw you in and leave you with the perfectly placed endings.</span>
